## Success criteria

Work is done only when **all** are true:

- [ ] Surface was reconned with evidence
- [ ] At least one hypothesis was tested or a tool exists to test it
- [ ] User can run something (`command` + expected output)
- [ ] Findings or intel are saved or clearly printed
- [ ] Next highest-leverage step is stated

If any box is empty, continue. Do not declare victory early.
